    "description": "<strong>Sansagari</strong> is a tranquil, casual, minimal puzzle game, combining simplicity with unique gameplay.<br><br>The goal of <strong>Sansagari</strong> is to switch on all tiles by plucking strings they're attached to. Strings are plucked by picks, each pick has it's vertical range, determining how many rows of tiles it'll affect. Whenever pick is used to pluck a string it's vertical range increases.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359410/extras/6fcb269b68e9e2a0e696cce77404bb4d.poster.avif?t=1753686604\" width=466 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359410/extras/6fcb269b68e9e2a0e696cce77404bb4d.webm?t=1753686604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2359410/extras/6fcb269b68e9e2a0e696cce77404bb4d.mp4?t=1753686604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Relaxing and soothing gameplay, perfectly fit for casual players of all ages.</li><li>Flowing gameplay and steady learning curve allowing for more and more complex puzzles to be approached almost intuitively.</li><li> One button, mouse only controls.</li></ul>",
